    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted given the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 single-condition protocol and the overall strength of the validation evidence. E/uval metrics below 1.96 for all QoIs; percentage differences within 10% acceptance bound. Overall credibility sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
